des: It’s hard to balance a full-time job with passion projects. Frankie Styles, self proclaimed creative to lazy to create, shares his struggles, accomplishments and more within is own personal life. If you have a side hustle, want to start a passion project, just want to hear some great career advice, or want to know you're not alone this is the podcast for you.
